|---|---|---|
| **Security headers** | None set | Added `helmet()` middleware |
| **Rate limiting** | No DoS protection | Added `express-rate-limit` |
| **Body parsing** | Missing | Added `express.json()` with `10kb` size limit |
| **Fingerprinting** | `X-Powered-By: Express` leaks server info | `app.disable('x-powered-by')` |
| **PII exposure** | Emails returned without auth | Removed sensitive fields; noted need for auth |
| **404 handling** | Unknown routes return default Express HTML | Added JSON 404 handler |
| **Global error handler** | Missing — errors crash or leak stack traces | Added 4-argument error middleware |
| **Error forwarding** | Routes don't catch/forward errors | Added `try/catch` + `next(err)` in routes |
| **Stack trace leaks** | N/A (no error handler existed) | Production mode returns generic message only |
| **Port config** | Hardcoded `3000` | Reads from `PORT` env var with `parseInt` validation |

