## Review of `app.js` — Error Handling, Input Validation & Security

### Current Issues

**1. No body parser or input validation middleware**
The app has no middleware to parse request bodies or validate input. If you add POST/PUT routes later, you'll need this — and it should be set up with size limits to prevent denial-of-service attacks.

**2. No global error handler**
